<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - GenCare</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #00796b;
            --secondary-color: #004d40;
            --text-color: #333;
            --background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        body {
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--background-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        header {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: space-between;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: white;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            letter-spacing: 1px;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 2rem auto;
            padding: 0 1.5rem;
        }

        .about-section {
            background: white;
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .about-section h2 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            font-size: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .about-content {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 2rem;
        }

        .about-text {
            flex: 1 1 60%;
        }

        .about-text p {
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .about-image {
            flex: 1 1 35%;
        }

        .about-image img {
            width: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }
.med-img-container {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
}

.animation-text {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    height: 1.5rem;
}

.cover-loaded {
    width: 98vw;
    height: 100vh;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: -2;
}

.overlay,
.overlay-name,
.overlay-p {
    position: absolute;
    color: #3c4e3d;
    font-size: 2.3333333333vw;
    z-index: 1;
    }

.overlay-name{
    top:10%;
    left:10%;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
}

.overlay {
    top: 30%;
    left: 50%; 
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-size: 2.3333333333vw;
    font-family: Scto Grotesk;
    text-align:center;
}

.overlay-p {
    top: 50%;
    left: 80%;
    font-size: 14px;
}

.explanation {
    padding: 1rem 12rem 1rem 12rem;

    text-wrap: pretty;
    background-color: #e7e4df;
    margin-top:-10;
    color: #3c4e3d;
}

.explanation .what-is {
    opacity: 0; 
    transform: translateX(-100px); 
    transition: opacity 3s ease, transform 3s ease;
    font-size: 30px;
  }
  
  .explanation .what-is.visible {
    opacity: 1; 
    transform: translateX(0); 
  }

.explanation .content {
    opacity: 0; 
    transform: translateX(-6rem); 
    transition: opacity 4s ease, transform 4s ease; 
  }
  
  .explanation .content.visible {
    opacity: 1; 
    transform: translateX(0); 
  }
  
  .core-attributes {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 3rem 0;
    opacity: 0; 
    transform: translateY(3rem);
    transition: all 0.6s ease-out;
  }
  
  .core-attributes.show {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  
  .core-attributes h1 {
    font-size: 2em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .boxes {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-template-rows: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
    justify-items: center;
  }
  
  .box {
    width: 28vw;
    height: 27vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    color: white;
    font-size: 1.2em;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(0.8);
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
    border-radius: 2rem;
    border: 0.1rem solid black;
    margin:0;
    background-color: #00796b;
  } 
  .top-left {
    transform-origin: left center;
  }
  
  .top-center {
    transform-origin: top center;
  }
  
  .top-right {
    transform-origin: right center;
  }
  
  .bottom-left {
    transform-origin: left bottom;
  }
  
  .bottom-center {
    transform-origin: bottom center;
  }
  
  .bottom-right {
    transform-origin: right bottom;
  }
  
  .box.show {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1);
  }
  
  .box.top-left.show {
    animation: slideInFromLeft 2s forwards;
  }
  
  .box.top-center.show {
    animation: slideInFromTop 2s forwards;
  }
  
  .box.top-right.show {
    animation: slideInFromRight 2s forwards;
  }
  
  .box.bottom-left.show {
    animation: slideInFromLeft 2s forwards;
  }
  
  .box.bottom-center.show {
    animation: slideInFromBottom 2s forwards;
  }
  
  .box.bottom-right.show {
    animation: slideInFromRight 2s forwards;
  }
  
  @keyframes slideInFromLeft {
    from {
      transform: translateX(-100%) scale(0.8);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(0) scale(1);
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes slideInFromTop {
    from {
      transform: translateY(-100%) scale(0.8);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes slideInFromRight {
    from {
      transform: translateX(100%) scale(0.8);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(0) scale(1);
    }
  }
  
  @keyframes slideInFromBottom {
    from {
      transform: translateY(100%) scale(0.8);
    }
    to {
      transform: translateY(0) scale(1);
    }
  }
  
  
  #dynamic-text {
    display: inline-block;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fadeIn 3s ease-in-out forwards;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  
  .additional-text {
    font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    color: #333;
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    display:flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap:2rem;
    opacity: 0;
    transition: opacity 1s;
  }

  .paracetamol img {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateX(-100%);
    transition: transform 1s ease, opacity 1s ease;
  }
  
  .additional-text.show {
    opacity: 1;
  }
  
  .additional-text.show .paracetamol img {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateX(0);
  }
  
  @keyframes fadeIn {
    0% {
      opacity: 0;
    }
    100% {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }
  

.header {
    text-align: center;
    background-color: #f7b5a6;
    padding: 2rem 1rem;
}

.title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin: 0;
}

.highlight {
    font-family: 'Brush Script MT', cursive;
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #333;
}

.about {
    padding: 2rem;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
}


.footer {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 1rem;
    background-color: #1e1e1e;
    color: #fff;
}

.footer a {
    color: #fff;
    text-decoration: none;
    margin: 0 0.5rem;
}

/* Dark Mode Styles */
body.dark-mode {
    background-color: #1e1e1e;
    color: #e0e0e0;
}

body.dark-mode header {
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #1f4037, #99f2c8);
}

body.dark-mode nav a {
    color: #b3ffab;
}
body.dark-mode .about-section {
    background-color: #1e1e1e;
    color: white;
}
body.dark-mode .explanation{
    background-color: #1e1e1e;
    color: #00796b;
}
body.dark-mode .content{
    color: white;
}


body.dark-mode footer {
    background-color: #1f4037;
}



</style>

<link rel="icon" href="assets/favicon.png" type="image/png">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="empty">

    </div>
    <header>
        About Us - GenCare
    </header>
    <button id="dark-mode-toggle">Toggle Dark Mode</button>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="about-section">
            <h2>Who We Are</h2>
            <div class="about-content">
                <div class="about-text">
                    <p>At GenCare, we are committed to empowering individuals with easy access to affordable and generic medicines. Our mission is to bridge the gap between quality healthcare and cost-effective solutions by providing transparent information and innovative tools.</p>
                    <p>We believe that healthcare is a right, not a privilege. Through our platform, we strive to create awareness, simplify choices, and make medicine accessible to everyone, everywhere.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/400x300" alt="Team working together">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

  
    
</section>
    <footer>
        &copy; 2024 GenCare. All rights reserved.
    </footer>
</body>

<script>

    //js for darkmode

        const darkModeToggle = document.getElementById('dark-mode-toggle');
        darkModeToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
            document.body.classList.toggle('dark-mode');
        });


    
</script>
</html>